OL,3,CMan who stabbed pregnant woman in
OL,4,CAberfan admits attempted murder
OL,6,FA 29-year-old man has admitted the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of a pregnant woman
OL,8,Fin Aberfan.
OL,10,FDaniel Popescu, of no fixed abode,
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to the attempted murder
OL,12,Fof Andrea Pintilli in Aberfan, Merthyr
OL,13,FTydfil, on December 5, 2023.
OL,15,FThe village of Aberfan was brought to
OL,16,Fa standstill on 5 December last year,
OL,17,Fwith emergency services called to the
OL,18,Fscene around 9.10am and schools going
OL,19,Finto lockdown as armed police searched
OL,20,Ffor the knifeman.
