OL,6,FThe victim was discharged from
OL,7,Fhospital in the days after the attack.
OL,9,FPopescu appeared in Cardiff Crown
OL,10,FCourt on Thursday, 4 April, where he
OL,11,Falso admitted a stalking offence.
OL,13,FThe defendant denied a further charge
OL,14,Fof intimidation, which the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service is not seeking a
OL,16,Ftrial over given the guilty plea to
OL,17,Fattempted murder.
OL,19,FPopescu is due to be sentenced on May
OL,20,F28.
